OL,3,CWhy canal remains shut months after
OL,4,Ctoxic chemical spill
OL,6,FThe towpath reopened in October, after
OL,7,F90kg of dead fish were removed, but
OL,8,Fboaters are still unable to access
OL,9,Fnorth of Ocker Hill junction to the
OL,10,Fjunction with the Wyrley and Essington
OL,11,FCanal.
OL,13,FIt is understood the Canal and River
OL,14,FTrust is waiting for the results of an
OL,15,Fecological report.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, the Environment Agency said
OL,18,Fpollution levels had reduced to an
OL,19,F"acceptable level", however it said
OL,20,Fpeople should still avoid contact with
OL,21,Fthe water.
