OL,3,CWhy canal remains shut months after
OL,4,Ctoxic chemical spill
OL,6,FAnochrome Ltd confirmed the spill in
OL,7,FAugust saying: "We can confirm that a
OL,8,Fchemical incident occurred at
OL,9,FAnochrome Ltd Walsall in the early
OL,10,Fhours of Monday, 12 August 2024.
OL,12,F"Regrettably, as a result, some of the
OL,13,Freleased chemicals entered a canal in
OL,14,FWalsall. Our immediate response was to
OL,15,Fnotify the Environment Agency and
OL,16,FSevern Trent Water.
