OL,3,CWhy canal remains shut months after
OL,4,Ctoxic chemical spill
OL,6,F"Our senior management team has been `
OL,7,Fand remain - on-site working
OL,8,Fcollaboratively with all relevant
OL,9,Fauthorities and agencies to minimise
OL,10,Fand contain the spill.
OL,12,F"In addition, from the moment we were
OL,13,Faware of the incident, we have made
OL,14,Fall our facilities available to the
OL,15,Fauthorities and agencies in
OL,16,Fattendance, including in-house
OL,17,Flaboratory testing facilities."
